<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000607/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The final mark will be formed by averaging the marks corresponding to the following items: practical questions and problems in Moodle (MOOD), reports of simulation & laboratory (SIM), and the exam (EX). The student passes the subjet if 0.50*EX+0.45*SIM+0.05*MOOD>5
REMARK: In case of need because of health and security reasons, the teaching and assessment activities will take place telematically."""@es ;
